          <br />
          Your appliances are an investment—we protect them using genuine manufacturer parts that meet original specifications for safety, longevity, and performance.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>✅ Same-Day or Next-Day Service</strong>
          <br />
          We offer priority scheduling in Glendale and always arrive on time, with full respect for your time, privacy, and space.
        </li>

