          <strong>✅ Discreet, White-Glove Repair Experience</strong>
          <br />
          We wear protective gear, maintain clean workspaces, and communicate with the level of professionalism expected in Glendale’s luxury homes, hillside residences, and carefully designed kitchens.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

