      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Book Your Appointment</strong>
          <br />
          Call or schedule online. We’ll confirm your preferred time and gather basic info about your appliance.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>On-Time Arrival & Brand-Specific Diagnosis</strong>
          <br />
          Your trained Luxury Appliance Repair by ZARICCI technician arrives promptly and performs a detailed inspection using specialized diagnostic tools.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Clear, Upfront Estimate</strong>
          <br />
          We walk you through the issue and provide a transparent quote—no pressure, no surprises.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Precision Repair Using OEM Parts</strong>
          <br />
          We complete the repair using authentic parts, restore function, and run comprehensive performance testing.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Final Walkthrough & Service Warranty</strong>
          <br />
          We clean up, answer your questions, and back our work with a warranty—because confidence is part of the experience.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Serving Glendale’s Distinctive Neighborhoods</h3>

      <p>
        We serve Glendale residences throughout Rossmoyne, Verdugo Woodlands, Chevy Chase Canyon, Glenoaks Canyon, Emerald Isle, Montecito Park, Adams Hill, Northwest Glendale, and the residential streets surrounding Brand Boulevard and Glenoaks Boulevard. Our service is designed for historic homes, custom hillside properties, modern condominiums, and luxury kitchens where careful diagnostics, clean workmanship, and discretion matter.
      </p>
    </section>

